genresAdvancedInfo.name: grunneger muziek
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This music genre originates from the northern region of the Netherlands and is sung in the Gronings dialect. It is characterized by its traditional folk sound and often features accordion and fiddle. The lyrics typically focus on everyday life in the Groningen province and the culture of the region.
